  "body": "For the Status Community Curation dApp, poll responses and votes are signed using [EIP-712](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-712): Ethereum typed structured data hashing and signing.\r\n\r\nCurrently, the data is displayed in one line JSON format:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/300805/131761492-ddaa8534-155a-40d3-91fb-c91f6b0c9a44.png)\r\n\r\nInstead, we should display the data in a more human readable format.\r\n\r\nThe [EIP-712](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-712) provides examples such as:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/300805/131761569-345fb1ae-7e49-4bf2-bfe9-11d3820f2f86.png)\r\n\r\nhttps://status-im.github.io/js-waku/eth-pm/ can be used to play around (broadcast encryption public key step).",
